iscountAmount}}","result_btn":"Shop now","reward_title":"You got the best prize","unlogin_reward_sub_title":"Sign in to claim it","login_reward_sub_title":"Click to claim it","reward_btn":"Claim now","reward_countdown_prefix":"Ends in","reward_off":"OFF","reward_tip":"Orders {{minAmount}}+ capped at {{maxDiscountAmount}}","reward_widget_off":"OFF","reward_widget_countdown_prefix":"Ends in","reward_widget_get_now":"GET NOW","rule_entry":"Rules","title_bg":"https://aimg.kwcdn.com/upload_aimg/material_res/aa8ce068-de68-4835-a25d-d510c9fc50e6.png.slim.png","sub_title_one":"SPIN TO","sub_title_two":"GET A COUPON","tip":"{{randomNum}}% offers claimed. Hurry up!","spin":"SPIN","turntable_off":"OFF","up_to":"UP to","up_num":"{{num}}% OFF","get_now":"GET NOW","rule_title":"Special offer rules","rule_content":"<div><p> </p>Limit one Offer per user for one order. Offer subjects to the time limit and other conditions as displayed on the page.</div><div><p> </p>Consumers must pay shipping fees (unless free shipping applied) and sales tax.</div><div><p> </p>Not valid in conjunction with any other coupon or offer.</div><div><p> </p>Offers are not transferrable or redeemable for cash.</div><div><p> </p>Improper use constitutes fraud. Offer not properly used or will be void.</div>","rule_ok":"OK","new_users_only":"New users only","not_new_user_fail_sub_title":"You are not eligible for this coupon.","result_new_user_title":"The coupon is only available for new user.","result_new_user_extra":"Extra bonus for you！","result_new_user_off":"{{offNum}}% OFF","new_user_reward_tip":"Orders {{minAmount}}, capped at {{maxDiscountAmount}}","new_user_gift":"New user gift","btn_ok":"ok","opps":"opps","no_new_user_reward_tips":"Sorry, the coupon is only avalible for new user","congrats":"Congrats! You got","rebateDesc":"Rebate"},"wigs-home-reviews":[{"score":5,"goodsId":601099513663000,"comment":"This my first time ordering a wig from here & ilove ittt!!! It's soo soft and it doesn't shed, & it is the exact length i wanted. i am very satisfied Temuuuu🥰","name":"hudsonjada503","reviewTime":"yesterday","time":"Mar 31, 2023","picture":"https://aimg.kwcdn.com/upload_aimg/kuiper/b35dfb94-5dcf-4869-b563-7973527c36be.jpeg.slim.jpeg"},{"score":5,"goodsId":601099512509824,"comment":"Hair is great, the lace was great as well. If you use a wide tooth comb there shouldn't be any shedding because it is deep wave hair but overall I love this wig !!","name":"Minnie606","time":"Apr 10, 2023","picture":"https://aimg.kwcdn.com/upload_aimg/kuiper/d2650d8d-5da9-4765-8f64-a35dd323896e.jpeg.slim.jpeg"},{"score":5,"goodsId":6017592186095910,"comment":"GREAT quality & lace! highly recommend! knots bleached well!","name":"Kylahhh777","time":"Feb 23, 2023","picture":"https://aimg.kwcdn.com/upload_aimg/kuiper/368b2d0f-47a0-442a-ba06-470bc1740db2.jpeg.slim.jpeg"},{"score":5,"goodsId":601099514724567,"comment":"Definitely recommend getting this pretty nice soft wig😍😍. Comes in a really cute package I adored it so much🥰. I've had this installed for a week and a half now and it still looks good and the hair texture is still good.","name":"Jimena","reviewTime":"yesterday","time":"Dec 15, 2022","picture":"https://aimg.kwcdn.com/upload_aimg/kuiper/5189c277-e6a9-4cb1-986e-063989d289cb.jpeg.slim.jpeg"},{"score":5,"goodsId":601099513897763,"comment":"I love it😍😍 the quality, everything!!! can't wait to get it installed!!!","name":"Amy Gueye","time":"Jan 8, 2023","picture":"https://aimg.kwcdn.com/upload_aimg/kuiper/c922347b-de22-476e-b4d3-14b935ae8d6f.jpeg.slim.jpeg"},{"score":5,"goodsId":601099512729931,"comment":"Love the texture and the color and fit, it is just like the picture shows.Thank you so much!","name":"Kayunjanae","time":"Mar 15, 2023","picture":"https://aimg.kwcdn.com/upload_aimg/kuiper/266f6c84-7d55-4a63-8cc7-197444869c9e.jpeg.slim.jpeg"},{"score":5,"goodsId":601099513087125,"comment":"Absolutely Beautiful!!Where do I start? I absolutely love this wig so TEMU Thank you guys I only spent 10 bucks roughly under 20 bucks for a quality wig so if you have questions about this week, I say buy it.No smell!!Fast Delivery!","name":"diordreamzz","time":"Apr 13, 2023","picture":"https://aimg.kwcdn.com/upload_aimg/kuiper/7fd0e264-b820-42a2-93ff-3e9c702a37df.jpeg.slim.jpeg"},{"score":5,"goodsId":601099512530533,"comment":"This wig is really cute for the price. No shedding and nice bounce to it.","name":"Rihana Watts","reviewTime":"yesterday","time":"Feb 10, 2023","picture":"https://aimg.kwcdn.com/upload_aimg/kuiper/eb37751a-6423-4bee-80b6-812ef5a3eb56.jpeg.slim.jpeg"},{"score":5,"goodsId":601099513774702,"comment":"Hair is sooo soft, can be curled & styled. Definitely buying again!!","name":"Cynthiaedegbe","time":"Apr 6, 2023","picture":"https://aimg.kwcdn.com/upload_aimg/kuiper/d4126e07-5ca1-40a0-a685-652defa7cdf3.jpeg.slim.jpeg"},{"score":5,"goodsId":601099513678454,"comment":"In love!!!!!! Great quality!!!! I recommend it 100/100","name":"nunuG999","reviewTime":"yesterday","time":"Mar 18, 2023","picture":"https://aimg.kwcdn.com/upload_aimg/kuiper/40848681-1551-4fd2-a8f7-ac48727557fd.jpeg.slim.jpeg"}],"women-cloth-home-reviews":[{"score":5,"goodsId":601099512215683,"comment":"OMGoodness!! These are so buttery soft! I am getting ready to purchase more in different colors! LOVE EVERYTHING ABOUT THEM! I am 5'6 140lbs. I bought the L(8/10). I washed and dried them in the dryer and the length, for me, is perfect. They are high waisted, which I like because, that way, you don't get that muffin top.","name":"msteed5260","reviewTime":"yesterday","time":"Feb 1, 2023","picture":"https://aimg.kwcdn.com/upload_aimg/kuiper/0fb52c47-00f2-4276-ad28-d3b79cb6478e.jpeg.slim.jpeg"},{"score":5,"goodsId":601099512047019,"comment":"Got a lot of compliments and I love the material.😍","name":"Regina Douglas","time":"Apr 24, 2023","picture":"https://aimg.kwcdn.com/upload_aimg/kuiper/c60359eb-771b-4607-82f7-fce8b9522e25.jpeg.slim.jpeg"},{"score":5,"goodsId":601099511749383,"comment":"This size S fits my daughter perfectly. She's 5'2, about 110 lbs. She likes to wear it both on and off her shoulders. The sweater is soft and very good quality, just like the photo. I might buy the other colors too.","name":"Martha Pongracic","time":"Feb 17, 2023","picture":"https://aimg.kwcdn.com/upload_aimg/kuiper/8bd1ecdc-3ba2-44bf-8bf1-2cca0886d4c1.jpeg.slim.jpeg"},{"score":5,"goodsId":601099513141741,"comment":"Pleasantly surprised. This is super cute and soft leather like feel. I'm not really a purse person but this honestly makes me happy.","name":"ellagsellentin","reviewTime":"yesterday","time":"Apr 15, 2023","picture":"https://aimg.kwcdn.com/upload_aimg/kuiper/d888232a-365b-4dd6-b029-3329920be39a.jpeg.slim.jpeg"},{"score":5,"goodsId":601099513347659,"comment":"Very nice dress. it is a shirter dress and hit me about 2 inches above the knee. I am 5'8 and weigh about 135lb if this helps others to kinda see how it will fit. i ordered the medium size 6 and it fit well. It does have a zipper back for easy removal.","name":"amadney","time":"Mar 30, 2023","picture":"https://aimg.kwcdn.com/upload_aimg/kuiper/5875211a-1b13-42a8-a77b-c5610d34b673.jpeg.slim.jpeg"},{"score":5,"goodsId":601099512501830,"comment":"Gorgeous dress.","name":"ivana777z","time":"Apr 16, 2023","picture":"https://aimg.kwcdn.com/upload_aimg/kuiper/6a0e8741-1fcc-4a12-9c43-1bf1ad5f99cf.jpeg.slim.jpeg"},{"score":5,"goodsId":6017592186137790,"comment":"I was impressed by the size, they are perfect, super comfortable I loved it 😍.","name":"A***l","time":"Apr 11, 2023","picture":"https://aimg.kwcdn.com/upload_aimg/kuiper/de8e3ed3-7f84-4f9c-b6d0-2b688c6adf69.jpeg.slim.jpeg"},{"score":5,"goodsId":601099512950428,"comment":"Beautiful! I am so pleased with it!","name":"Monica Roussin","reviewTime":"yesterday","time":"Apr 25, 2023","picture":"https://aimg.kwcdn.com/upload_aimg/kuiper/3ccc39df-fc3d-4dbc-8c1f-b586c36cac69.jpeg.slim.jpeg"},{"score":5,"goodsId":601099513181420,"comment":"True to size and super light. Can walk in them all day!","name":"Estrella Perez","time":"Apr 11, 2023","picture":"https://aimg.kwcdn.com/upload_aimg/kuiper/42645f36-1eec-48e4-8341-5e8fbf5d1ad3.jpeg.slim.jpeg"},{"score":5,"goodsId":601099513409939,"comment":"They're cute asf. They're a lil loose on me but at the same time hug my thighs good. Also they’re easy to put on.","name":"gen2stunny","reviewTime":"yesterday","time":"Mar 11, 2023","picture":"https://aimg.kwcdn.com/upload_aimg/kuiper/e4d76f52-0ff0-4a1a-9f50-051101d12e28.jpeg.slim.jpeg"}],"kol-coupon-banner":{"rules":"Rules","for_all_products":"For all products","coupon_benefit_discount":"{{discount}}% OFF","cps_free_shipping_benefit_name":"Free shipping","cps_free_return_benefit_name":"Free returns","for_new_user":"FOR NEW USER","for_new_user_1":"For new user","only_for_new_user":"only for new user","code":"CODE","min_amount":"No min, ","no_min_amount":"Orders over {{currencyDisplay}}{{minAmount}}, ","coupon_benefit_capped":"capped at {{currencyDisplay}}{{maxDiscountAmount}}","copy":"Copy","ends_in":"Ends in","ends_in_v2":"Ends in","join_affiliate":"Join Affiliate Program to earn {{currencyDisplay}}{{amount}}","go":"GO","claim":"Claim","code_copied_successfully":"Code copied successfully","claimed_successfully":"Claimed successfully","join":"Join","new_user":"New Users","get_up_to":"Get up to {{currencyDisplay}}{{maxDiscountAmount}} Off","off":"% OFF","got_it":"Got it","congrat":"Congrats! You got","new_app_user":"New App Users Only","coupon":"Coupon","extra":"Extra Coupon","dnld_text":"Download Temu App to claim","scan_text":"Scan the QR code with your phone","off_v2":" OFF","code_v2":"Code","capped_at":"Orders over {{currencyDisplay}}{{minAmount}},capped at ","join_affiliate_text":"Join Affiliate Program to earn","used":"Used","expired":"Expired","unqualified":"Unqualified","get_up_to_v2":"Get up to {{maxDiscountAmount}} Off","capped_at_v2":"Orders over {{minAmount}},capped at ","affiliate_banner":"https://aimg.kwcdn.com/uplo